snippet.title: Just Cause 4 – Official Launch Trailer [ESRB]
snippet.description:
Buy Just Cause 4 NOW! https://bit.ly/2reMrkw
 
The wait is over! Just Cause 4 is now available on PlayStation 4, Xbox One, and PC. The vast South American open world of Solís is now waiting for you. 


Take advantage of Rico’s unique set of weapons and gadgets, and fight your enemies in extreme weather conditions. It’s time to bring the thunder!
